OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F426A1773238282
OL,3,CThree more arrested on suspicion of
OL,4,Cmurder after man dies in alleyway
OL,6,FEmergency services were called to the
OL,7,Fscene just after 8pm on Friday to
OL,8,Ftreat a man who had sustained serious
OL,9,Finjuries.
OL,11,FHe died just over an hour later.
OL,13,FChief Inspector John Bonner said:
OL,14,F"Whilst I understand this incident has
OL,15,Fno doubt caused some concern in the
OL,16,Flocal community, at this stage we
OL,17,Fbelieve this was isolated and targeted
OL,18,Fincident.
OL,26,@vD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/4
