FL,427,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F426A1773238282
OL,3,CThree more arrested on suspicion of
OL,4,Cmurder after man dies in alleyway
OL,6,F"Extensive enquiries are ongoing and
OL,7,FI'd urge people not to speculate
OL,8,Fonline whilst our investigation
OL,9,Fcontinues. There will continue to be a
OL,10,Flarge police presence in the area so
OL,11,Fplease if you have any concerns speak
OL,12,Fto our officers.
OL,14,F"If you have not yet spoken with
OL,15,Fpolice but have information you think
OL,16,Fmay help with our investigation,
OL,17,Fplease contact us on 101 number,
OL,18,Fquoting reference number 042669. We'd
OL,19,Falso appeal for anyone with any
OL,20,Frelevant dash cam or private CCTV
OL,21,Ffootage."
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOU}D@IO]
